\r\n上訴審判裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　11　　月　　 2　　日\r\n                              書記官　謝鎮光","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PTEV/111%2c%e5%b1%8f%e5%b0%8f%2c315%2c20221102%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PTEV,111,屏小,315,20221102,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"屏小","JNO":"315","JDATE":"20221102","JTITLE":"清償借款"}